title: The Inspector General (1949).mkv
description:
DVD Rip (Roan Group Version)
Resolution: 720x482
Format: MKV

As far as I know, this is the best version of this movie out (Roan Group).  I went through pains to get this version and tried to keep as much of it's integrity as possible.  That said, it's admittedly rough looking when compared to more contemporary movies.  Still funny though.

I'll probably seed for a few weeks and see how it goes.  If there's interest, I'll drop by every once and a while to top it off
